tariffs and trade or gatt 
the agreement could lead to a doubling of us exports of beef 
and oranges by 1991 to more than 1 billion a year in return the 
united states agreed to withdraw its gatt complaint against japans 
restrictive import quotas 
yeutter said the complaint and previous success under gatt 
rules last year helped prod japan into accepting an expansion of 
beef and citrus imports 
in other words the jig was up he said theyd gotten 
