tougher and more creative policies and penalties martinez said 
we must make the cost of drug trafficking and drug abuse so high 
that individuals wont risk getting involved 
martinez said he wanted the new chairman and 15member task 
force to consider such options as using the florida national guard 
including its air unit to help locate illicit drug shipments into 
the state the national guard is now used in a minor role in 
surveillance 
