believed to come through florida which has more than 1350 miles 
of coastline 
he also recommended that a task force look at random drug tests 
for most state employees especially those who work in the states 
schools in the prisons and on the highways 
he also said the task force would consider extending the death 
penalty statute to major traffickers and drug dealers 
