<TEXT>
a landslide in southern china has killed 14 
people and seven others are missing a newspaper reported thursday 
the official peoples daily remnin ribao said the landslide in 
the village of xiayuan in southern chinas jiangxi province tuesday 
covered nearly 10 acres of land with mud and stone and destroyed 29 
houses 
thirtyseven people were seriously injured the report said 
the report did not say what caused the landslide 
