examiner in 2inch type and the parade route was clogged with 
vendors hawking tshirts pennants and hats 
the lakers with a 108105 victory over the detroit pistons in 
game 7 of the national basketball association championship series 
tuesday night became the first team to win backtoback titles 
since the 1969 celtics 
