weekends in different cities every three months he said one recent 
trip to san francisco booked through easterns club cost 175 
round trip the cheapest comparable airfare i was able to find 
was 268 he said 
but seiler concedes you have to have a job that allows you to 
pick up at a weeks notice and you have to have freedom im just 
very flexible 
people think theyre more flexible than they really are 
said vacations to go president alan fox adding that only about 10 
percent of his companys members actually go on at least one 
advertised trip a year 
